### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### Submit PA Request — Clear Approval Case (Physical Therapy)
POST http://localhost:8000/pa/submit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "member_id": "MBR-2026-001",
  "provider_npi": "1234567890",
  "diagnosis_codes": ["M54.5"],
  "procedure_codes": ["97110"],
  "service_description": "Physical therapy evaluation and treatment for low back pain",
  "clinical_notes": "Patient presents with chronic low back pain, duration 6 months. Conservative treatment (NSAIDs, home exercise) has not provided adequate relief. Requesting 12 sessions of physical therapy.",
  "urgency": "standard",
  "lob": "commercial"
}

### Submit PA Request — Ambiguous Case (Advanced Imaging)
POST http://localhost:8000/pa/submit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "member_id": "MBR-2026-002",
  "provider_npi": "9876543210",
  "diagnosis_codes": ["M79.3"],
  "procedure_codes": ["72148"],
  "service_description": "MRI lumbar spine without contrast",
  "clinical_notes": "Patient reports intermittent low back pain for 2 weeks. No radiculopathy. No prior imaging or conservative treatment attempted.",
  "urgency": "standard",
  "lob": "commercial"
}

### Check PA Status
GET http://localhost:8000/pa/status/{{request_id}}

### Dashboard
GET http://localhost:8000/pa/dashboard
